!!//字符串(string)转换为DateTime类型的三种方法//
* //Convert.ToDateTime(string)//
** string 格式：//yyyy-mm-dd hh:mm:ss//
* //Convert.ToDateTime(string, IFormatProvider)//
* //~~DateTime.ParseExact()~~//

!!//1、Convert.ToDateTime(string)//
!!!要求格式：//`yyyy-mm-dd hh:mm:ss`//


!!//2、Convert.ToDateTime(string, `IFormatProvider`)//
```c
DateTimeFormatInfo dateTimeFormat = new DateTimeFormatInfo();
dateTimeFormat.ShortDatePattern = "yyyy/MM/dd hh:mm:ss";
DateTime dateTimeTemp = Convert.ToDateTime(dateTimes, dateTimeFormat);
```


!!3、~~DateTime.ParseExact()~~
```c
DateTime dateTimeTemp = DateTime.ParseExact(dateTimes, "yyyy/MM/dd hh:mm:ss", CultureInfo.CurrentCulture);
return dateTimeTemp;
```

        "$:/language/Help/fetch": {
            "title": "$:/language/Help/fetch",
            "description": "Fetch tiddlers from wiki by URL",
            "text": "Fetch one or more files over HTTP/HTTPS, and import the tiddlers matching a filter, optionally transforming the incoming titles.\n\n```\n--fetch file <url> <import-filter> <transform-filter>\n--fetch files <url-filter> <import-filter> <transform-filter>\n--fetch raw-file <url> <transform-filter>\n--fetch raw-files <url-filter> <transform-filter>\n```\n\nThe \"file\" and \"files\" variants fetch the specified files and attempt to import the tiddlers within them (the same processing as if the files were dragged into the browser window). The \"raw-file\" and \"raw-files\" variants fetch the specified files and then store the raw file data in tiddlers, without applying the import logic.\n\nWith the \"file\" and \"raw-file\" variants only a single file is fetched and the first parameter is the URL of the file to read.\n\nWith the \"files\" and \"raw-files\" variants, multiple files are fetched and the first parameter is a filter yielding a list of URLs of the files to read. For example, given a set of tiddlers tagged \"remote-server\" that have a field \"url\" the filter `[tag[remote-server]get[url]]` will retrieve all the available URLs.\n\nFor the \"file\" and \"files\" variants, the `<import-filter>` parameter specifies a filter determining which tiddlers are imported. It defaults to `[all[tiddlers]]` if not provided.\n\nFor all variants, the `<transform-filter>` parameter specifies an optional filter that transforms the titles of the imported tiddlers. For example, `[addprefix[$:/myimports/]]` would add the prefix `$:/myimports/` to each title.\n\nPreceding the `--fetch` command with `--verbose` will output progress information during the import.\n\nNote that TiddlyWiki will not fetch an older version of an already loaded plugin.\n\nThe following example retrieves all the non-system tiddlers from https://tiddlywiki.com and saves them to a JSON file:\n\n```\ntiddlywiki --verbose --fetch file \"https://tiddlywiki.com/\" \"[!is[system]]\" \"\" --rendertiddler \"$:/core/templates/exporters/JsonFile\" output.json text/plain \"\" exportFilter \"[!is[system]]\"\n```\n\nThe following example retrieves the \"favicon\" file from tiddlywiki.com and saves it in a file called \"output.ico\". Note that the intermediate tiddler \"Icon Tiddler\" is quoted in the \"--fetch\" command because it is being used as a transformation filter to replace the default title, while there are no quotes for the \"--savetiddler\" command because it is being used directly as a title.\n\n```\ntiddlywiki --verbose --fetch raw-file \"https://tiddlywiki.com/favicon.ico\" \"[[Icon Tiddler]]\" --savetiddler \"Icon Tiddler\" output.ico\n```\n\n"
        },

        "$:/language/Help/import": {
            "title": "$:/language/Help/import",
            "description": "Import tiddlers from a file",
            "text": "Import tiddlers from TiddlyWiki (`.html`), `.tiddler`, `.tid`, `.json` or other local files. The deserializer must be explicitly specified, unlike the `load` command which infers the deserializer from the file extension.\n\n```\n--import <filepath> <deserializer> [<title>] [<encoding>]\n```\n\nThe deserializers in the core include:\n\n* application/javascript\n* application/json\n* application/x-tiddler\n* application/x-tiddler-html-div\n* application/x-tiddlers\n* text/html\n* text/plain\n\nThe title of the imported tiddler defaults to the filename.\n\nThe encoding defaults to \"utf8\", but can be \"base64\" for importing binary files.\n\nNote that TiddlyWiki will not import an older version of an already loaded plugin.\n"
        },
        "$:/language/Help/init": {
            "title": "$:/language/Help/init",
            "description": "Initialise a new wiki folder",
            "text": "Initialise an empty [[WikiFolder|WikiFolders]] with a copy of the specified edition.\n\n```\n--init <edition> [<edition> ...]\n```\n\nFor example:\n\n```\ntiddlywiki ./MyWikiFolder --init empty\n```\n\nNote:\n\n* The wiki folder directory will be created if necessary\n* The \"edition\" defaults to ''empty''\n* The init command will fail if the wiki folder is not empty\n* The init command removes any `includeWikis` definitions in the edition's `tiddlywiki.info` file\n* When multiple editions are specified, editions initialised later will overwrite any files shared with earlier editions (so, the final `tiddlywiki.info` file will be copied from the last edition)\n* `--editions` returns a list of available editions\n"
        },
        "$:/language/Help/listen": {
            "title": "$:/language/Help/listen",
            "description": "Provides an HTTP server interface to TiddlyWiki",
            "text": "Serves a wiki over HTTP.\n\nThe listen command uses NamedCommandParameters:\n\n```\n--listen [<name>=<value>]...\n```\n\nAll parameters are optional with safe defaults, and can be specified in any order. The recognised parameters are:\n\n* ''host'' - optional hostname to serve from (defaults to \"127.0.0.1\" aka \"localhost\")\n* ''path-prefix'' - optional prefix for paths\n* ''port'' - port number on which to listen; non-numeric values are interpreted as a system environment variable from which the port number is extracted (defaults to \"8080\")\n* ''credentials'' - pathname of credentials CSV file (relative to wiki folder)\n* ''anon-username'' - the username for signing edits for anonymous users\n* ''username'' - optional username for basic authentication\n* ''password'' - optional password for basic authentication\n* ''authenticated-user-header'' - optional name of header to be used for trusted authentication\n* ''readers'' - comma separated list of principals allowed to read from this wiki\n* ''writers'' - comma separated list of principals allowed to write to this wiki\n* ''csrf-disable'' - set to \"yes\" to disable CSRF checks (defaults to \"no\")\n* ''root-tiddler'' - the tiddler to serve at the root (defaults to \"$:/core/save/all\")\n* ''root-render-type'' - the content type to which the root tiddler should be rendered (defaults to \"text/plain\")\n* ''root-serve-type'' - the content type with which the root tiddler should be served (defaults to \"text/html\")\n* ''tls-cert'' - pathname of TLS certificate file (relative to wiki folder)\n* ''tls-key'' - pathname of TLS key file (relative to wiki folder)\n* ''debug-level'' - optional debug level; set to \"debug\" to view request details (defaults to \"none\")\n* ''gzip'' - set to \"yes\" to enable gzip compression for some http endpoints (defaults to \"no\")\n\nFor information on opening up your instance to the entire local network, and possible security concerns, see the WebServer tiddler at TiddlyWiki.com.\n\n"
        },

        "$:/language/Help/render": {
            "title": "$:/language/Help/render",
            "description": "Renders individual tiddlers to files",
            "text": "Render individual tiddlers identified by a filter and save the results to the specified files.\n\nOptionally, the title of a template tiddler can be specified. In this case, instead of directly rendering each tiddler, the template tiddler is rendered with the \"currentTiddler\" variable set to the title of the tiddler that is being rendered.\n\nA name and value for an additional variable may optionally also be specified.\n\n```\n--render <tiddler-filter> [<filename-filter>] [<render-type>] [<template>] [<name>] [<value>]\n```\n\n* ''tiddler-filter'': A filter identifying the tiddler(s) to be rendered\n* ''filename-filter'': Optional filter transforming tiddler titles into pathnames. If omitted, defaults to `[is[tiddler]addsuffix[.html]]`, which uses the unchanged tiddler title as the filename\n* ''render-type'': Optional render type: `text/html` (the default) returns the full HTML text and `text/plain` just returns the text content (ie it ignores HTML tags and other unprintable material)\n* ''template'': Optional template through which each tiddler is rendered\n* ''name'': Name of optional variable\n* ''value'': Value of optional variable\n\nBy default, the filename is resolved relative to the `output` subdirectory of the edition directory. The `--output` command can be used to direct output to a different directory.\n\nNotes:\n\n* The output directory is not cleared of any existing files\n* Any missing directories in the path to the filename are automatically created.\n* When referring to a tiddler with spaces in its title, take care to use both the quotes required by your shell and also TiddlyWiki's double square brackets : `--render \"[[Motovun Jack.jpg]]\"`\n* The filename filter is evaluated with the selected items being set to the title of the tiddler currently being rendered, allowing the title to be used as the basis for computing the filename. For example `[encodeuricomponent[]addprefix[static/]]` applies URI encoding to each title, and then adds the prefix `static/`\n* The `--render` command is a more flexible replacement for both the `--rendertiddler` and `--rendertiddlers` commands, which are deprecated\n\nExamples:\n\n* `--render \"[!is[system]]\" \"[encodeuricomponent[]addprefix[tiddlers/]addsuffix[.html]]\"` -- renders all non-system tiddlers as files in the subdirectory \"tiddlers\" with URL-encoded titles and the extension HTML\n\n"
        },
        "$:/language/Help/rendertiddler": {
            "title": "$:/language/Help/rendertiddler",
            "description": "Render an individual tiddler as a specified ContentType",
            "text": "(Note: The `--rendertiddler` command is deprecated in favour of the new, more flexible `--render` command)\n\nRender an individual tiddler as a specified ContentType, defaulting to `text/html` and save it to the specified filename.\n\nOptionally the title of a template tiddler can be specified, in which case the template tiddler is rendered with the \"currentTiddler\" variable set to the tiddler that is being rendered (the first parameter value).\n\nA name and value for an additional variable may optionally also be specified.\n\n```\n--rendertiddler <title> <filename> [<type>] [<template>] [<name>] [<value>]\n```\n\nBy default, the filename is resolved relative to the `output` subdirectory of the edition directory. The `--output` command can be used to direct output to a different directory.\n\nAny missing directories in the path to the filename are automatically created.\n\nFor example, the following command saves all tiddlers matching the filter `[tag[done]]` to a JSON file titled `output.json` by employing the core template `$:/core/templates/exporters/JsonFile`.\n\n```\n--rendertiddler \"$:/core/templates/exporters/JsonFile\" output.json text/plain \"\" exportFilter \"[tag[done]]\"\n```\n"

            "text": "Legacy command to serve a wiki over HTTP.\n\n```\n--server <port> <root-tiddler> <root-render-type> <root-serve-type> <username> <password> <host> <path-prefix> <debug-level>\n```\n\nThe parameters are:\n\n* ''port'' - port number on which to listen; non-numeric values are interpreted as a system environment variable from which the port number is extracted (defaults to \"8080\")\n* ''root-tiddler'' - the tiddler to serve at the root (defaults to \"$:/core/save/all\")\n* ''root-render-type'' - the content type to which the root tiddler should be rendered (defaults to \"text/plain\")\n* ''root-serve-type'' - the content type with which the root tiddler should be served (defaults to \"text/html\")\n* ''username'' - the default username for signing edits\n* ''password'' - optional password for basic authentication\n* ''host'' - optional hostname to serve from (defaults to \"127.0.0.1\" aka \"localhost\")\n* ''path-prefix'' - optional prefix for paths\n* ''debug-level'' - optional debug level; set to \"debug\" to view request details (defaults to \"none\")\n\nIf the password parameter is specified then the browser will prompt the user for the username and password. It can be useful to use an environment variable to pass the port number to the Node.js process. </$transclude>

\end

Only a subset of these languages are supported by the plugin. It is possible for users to change the set of languages supported by the plugin by following these steps:\n \n# Go to the highlight.js project [[download page|https://highlightjs.org/download/]], select the language definitions to include, and press the Download button to download a zip archive containing customised support files for a highlight.js syntax highlighting server.\n# Locate the `highlight.pack.js` file in the highlight plugin -- on a stock Debian 8 system running Tiddlywiki5 under node-js it is located at `/usr/local/lib/node_modules/tiddlywiki/plugins/tiddlywiki/highlight/files/highlight.pack.js`.\n# Replace the plugin `highlight.pack.js` file located in step 2 with the one from the downloaded archive obtained in step 1.\n# Restart the Tiddlywiki server.\n"

        "$:/plugins/tiddlywiki/highlight/readme": {
            "title": "$:/plugins/tiddlywiki/highlight/readme",
            "text": "This plugin provides syntax highlighting of code blocks using v9.18.1 of [[highlight.js|https://github.com/isagalaev/highlight.js]] from Ivan Sagalaev.\n\n! Usage\n\nWhen the plugin is installed it automatically applies highlighting to all codeblocks defined with triple backticks or with the CodeBlockWidget.\n\nThe language can optionally be specified after the opening triple braces:\n\n<$codeblock code=\"\"\"```css\n * { margin: 0; padding: 0; } /* micro reset */\n\nhtml { font-size: 62.5%; }\nbody { font-size: 14px; font-size: 1.4rem; } /* =14px */\nh1   { font-size: 24px; font-size: 2.4rem; } /* =24px */\n```\"\"\"/>\n\nIf no language is specified highlight.js will attempt to automatically detect the language.\n\n! public class MainActivity extends AppCompatActivity {

        super.onCreate(savedInstanceState);
        setContentView(R.layout.activity_main);
    ……
```
* `MainActivity` 继承自 `AppCompatActivity`
* `onCreate()`方法：界面打开后，最先运行的地方
** 一般用来界面初始化、控件初始化、参数和变量初始化

!! //Manifests：配置文件//
```java
<activity android:name=".MainActivity">
    <intent-filter>
        <action android:name="android.intent.action.MAIN" />
        <category android:name="android.intent.category.LAUNCHER" />
    </intent-filter>
</activity>
```
* `activity` 配置界面；`Main`开机的第一个界面
* 该处用于：`添加界面`、`界面优先级`

<manifest xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android"
    package="com.example.hello">

    <application……
……
```

!! //添加字符串资源//
* `Android视图`查看文件，选择 `app > res > values > strings.xml`
* 添加字符串 `name_text`、`send_button`
```xml
<resources>
    <string name="app_name">HelloWorld</string>
    <string name="name_text">Zhang San</string>
    <string name="send_button">Say Hi</string>
</resources>
```

!! //修改视图资源//
* ''`EditText`''
** id：`@+id/name_edit_text`
** text：`@string/name_text`，即 ''`字符串资源`''
* ''`Button`''
** id：`@+id/send_button`
** text：`@string/send_button`

<LinearLayout

    <EditText……
    <Button……

!! //处理 Activity//
* //''效果：点击 Button，生成 Toast 显示 EditText 内容''//
* 打开 `app > java > com.example.helloAndroid > MainActivity`
* 声明 `EditText`、`Button`对象
** `private EditText mNameEditText;`
* `EditText`、`Button`对象 实例化
** mNameEditText = `(EditText) findViewById(R.id.name_edit_text);`
* `Button`对象设置监听器
** mSendButton.`setOnClickListener`
** `Toast.makeText(MainActivity.this, name_text, Toast.LENGTH_SHORT).show();`
```java
public class MainActivity extends AppCompatActivity {
    private EditText mNameEditText;
    private Button mSendButton;

    @Override
    protected void onCreate(Bundle savedInstanceState) {
        super.onCreate(savedInstanceState);
        setContentView(R.layout.activity_main);

        mNameEditText = (EditText) findViewById(R.id.name_edit_text);
        mSendButton = (Button) findViewById(R.id.send_button);
        mSendButton.setOnClickListener(new View.OnClickListener() {
            @Override
            public void onClick(View v) {
                String name_text = mNameEditText.getText().toString()();
                Toast.makeText(MainActivity.this, name_text, Toast.LENGTH_SHORT).show();
            }
        });
    }
}
```






!! 先验Demo：[[Android入门-Activity]]
!! //新建Activity//
* `app > java > com.example.helloAndroid > New > Activity > Empty Activity`，名为 `SayHiActivity`
* 新建字符串资源：`<string name="hi_text">Hi, %1$s!</string>`
* 布局文件`activity_say_hi.xml`中添加一个`TextView`
** `id="@+id/hi_text_view"`
** `layout_margin="0"`
** `text="@string/hi_text"`

!! //新建 intent//
* //''两个 Activity 之间需要通信，需使用 intent 传递信息''//
* MainActivity.java，创建 `EXTRA_NAME 变量`
```java
public static final String EXTRA_NAME = "com.mwangblog.helloworld.NAME";
```
* 修改`mSendButton`监听器，点击`Button`，启动 `SayHiActivity`
```java
mSendButton.setOnClickListener(new View.OnClickListener() {
    @Override
    public void onClick(View v) {
        String name_text = mNameEditText.getText().toString();
        Intent intent = new Intent (HelloWorldActivity.this, SayHiActivity.class);
        intent.putExtra(EXTRA_NAME, name_text);
        startActivity(intent);
    }
});
```

!! //接收 intent//
* 接收 intent，对字符串格式化，最后设置 mHiTextView
```java
protected void onCreate(Bundle savedInstanceState) {
    super.onCreate(savedInstanceState);
    setContentView(R.layout.activity_say_hi);

    Intent intent = getIntent();
    String name = intent.getStringExtra (HelloWorldActivity.EXTRA_NAME);

    String hi_text = getResources().getString(R.string.hi_text);
    String hi_name = String.format(hi_text, name);

    mHiTextView = (TextView) findViewById(R.id.hi_text_view);
    mHiTextView.setText(hi_name);
}
```

!! ''//帮助文档//''
* `name /?`，如`for /?`

!! ''//`for`命令//''
* ''//Syntax//''：`FOR %%variable IN (set) DO command [command-parameters]`
** bat文件中采用，//''`%%variable`''//，cmd采用 //''`%varibale`''//

!! ''//`/d`//''
* //''Syntax''//：`for /d %%var in (set) do command [command-parameters]`
* 如果//''`set`''//中包含通配符（* ?），仅匹配目录（文件夹），不匹配文件
** `for /d %%i in (d:\desktop\*) do echo %%i`

!! ''//`/r`//''
* //''Syntax''//：`for /r [[drive:]path] %%var in (set) do command [command parameters]`
* `for /r d:\temp\ %i in (*.exe) do echo %i`，//''d:\temp\''//路径下所有文件夹，检索//''exe''//文件
* `for /r %i in (*.exe) do echo %i`，cmd所在文件夹下，所有//''exe''//文件
* `@echo off && for /r d:\desktop\ %i in (beauty.mp3) do if exist %i echo %i && pause`，查找是否存在文件 ''//beauty.mp3//''

!! ''//`/l` 增量//'' 
* ''//Syntax//''：`for /l %%var in (start, step, end) do command [command-parameters]`
* `for /l %%i in(1,1,3) do start cmd`，打开`3`个CMD

!! ''//`/f` 文件解析//''
!! <$link to="bat依次读取txt每一行" class="badge-pill badge-info text-white">bat读取txt每一行</$link>
* //''Syntax''//：`for /f ["options"] %%var in (file-set) do command [command-parameters]`
* `["options"]`：令牌
** `FOR /F "eol=; tokens=1,3* delims=,- " %%i in (test.txt) do
echo %%i %%j %%k`
*** `eol=;` 分号开头的行为为注释行
*** `tokens=1,3*` 将每行第 1 段,第 3 段和剩余字段分别赋予变量
*** `delines=,- ` （减号后有一空格）以逗号减号和空格为分隔符


```bash
@echo off
rem 首先建立临时文件 test.txt
echo ;注释行,这是临时文件,用完删除 >test.txt
echo 11 段 12 段 13 段 14 段 15 段 16 段 >>test.txt
echo 21 段,22 段,23 段,24 段,25 段,26 段 >>test.txt
echo 31 段-32 段-33 段-34 段-35 段-36 段 >>test.txt
FOR /F "eol=; tokens=1,3* delims=,- " %%i in (test.txt) do
echo %%i %%j %%k
Pause
Del test.txt
```









!! ''//文件地址 url.txt；下载器 youtube-dl.exe//''


```bash
@echo off
echo please place 'url.txt' and 'youtube-dl.exe' in the same folder as this bat
echo pause
for /f "tokens=*" %%i in (url.txt) do (echo Start downloading && .\youtube-dl %%i)
timeout /t 5
```

* //''`批处理 bat文件，使用 %%i`''//
* `for /f "tokens=*" %i in (1.txt) do (echo %%i)`

!! //''外部命令、内部命令''//

! //''`外部程序的调用，需要call，否则仅执行一句，便停止运行`''//
<<<

* 内部命令：dir、copy、mv……
* 外部命令：位于`C:/Windows/system32`目录下的程序
* 通过将程序防止在 `system32` 目录下，扩展可使用的程序

!! ''//注释与命令显示//''

* `@echo off`：关闭命令显示
* 注释：`REM`：显示；`::`：不显示

!! ''//修改CMD标题//''
* ''//Synax：//''`title 这是命令行窗口的标题`

!! ''//Timeout 延时操作//''
* 延时`10s`：`timeout /T 10`

!! ''//清空命令行//''
* `cls`









!! ''//拷贝//''
* `/y`，用于提示是否`覆盖原有文件`时候，自动`确认`
```bash
copy /y D:\Temp\ToDo.html D:\Tiddly\Mememori.html
```

!! ''//文件夹拷贝//''
```bash
xcopy /?
xcopy 1 2

echo d|xcopy 1 2
```

!! ''//移动//''
```bash
move /y D:\Temp\ToDo.html D:\Tiddly\Mememori.html
```






!! ''//新建文件夹//''
* `md D:\desktop\newFolder\Folder`
* cmd切换至新建文件夹的根目录，`md Folder`

!! ''//删除文件夹//''
* `rd Folder`






!! ''//`@` 命令行回显//''
* `echo off`，关闭命令回显
* `@echo off`，关闭单条命令回显

!! ''//`%` 变量引导//''
* `%var%`，引用变量
* `%i`（i为数字），调用程序外部参数
** `%0`，自身；`%1`，第`1`个参数
** `copy %0 D:/desktop`，复制文件自身

!! ''//`>` 输出重定向（new）//''
* `echo hello > 1.txt`，创建1.txt，内容：`hello `（空格）
* `echo hell>1.txt`，创建1.txt，内容：`hello`

!! ''//`>>` 输出重定向（Append）//''


!! ''`|` //管道命令符//''，__''有风险''__
* //''Syntax''//：`第一条命令 | 第二条命令 [| 第三条命令……]`
** `echo.|time`
** `echo y|copy 1.txt 2.txt`

!! ''//`^` 转义符//''

!! ''//`""` 字符串界定符//''
* 以下效果一致

<<<
```bash
cd "progrma files"
cd progra~1
cd pro*
```

!! ''//Syntax：`Echo 答复语|命令文件名`//''

<<translink """bat文件复制粘贴""" >>

!! ''//回车`echo.`//''
* `echo.`，相当于输入回车
* `time`返回结果如下，按下`Enter`，向程序输入`回车`
* //''`echo.|time`''//简化上述操作
```powershell
当前时间: 10:56:03.39
输入新时间:
```






!! ''//bat时间//''
```bash
set a=%Date:~0,4%_%Date:~5,2%_%Date:~8,2%
echo %a%
```


!! ''//`echo a` 和 `echo %a%`//''
* `echo a`，输出`a`
* `echo %a%`，输出`变量a的值`

```bash
@echo off
@echo 标题
title bat命令行

@echo 获取系统年月日 其中~0,4 表示从第 0 位开始截取 4 个字符
set a=%Date:~0,4%_%Date:~5,2%_%Date:~8,2%
echo %a%
rem 获取时分秒
@echo 获取时分秒
echo %time:~0,2%%time:~3,2%%time:~6,2%
pause
```






!! ''//直接调用，需处于同一文件夹下//''
* `call`批处理程序；`start`外部程序
* `call 2.bat`
* `start explorer d:/`
!!! ''//`注意 command line程序的调用，在命令执行完毕后，command line程序便关闭`//''

!! ''//不同文件夹下调用//''
```bash
d:
cd d:/desktop
call 2.bat
```

!! ''//启动新的 cmd窗口//''
* `start “new cmd” cmd /k call 2.bat`
** 新建cmd窗口，名为：`new cmd`
** `/k`，执行完毕后保持`打开`；`/c`，执行完`关闭`

```bash
@echo off
echo start new cmd
cd d:/desktop
start "new cmd" cmd /k call 2.bat
```







!! ''//外部程序调用，仅执行一次，便终止//''
* 以下代码，执行完`tiddlywiki`，并不执行`d: & cd d:/desktop `
```bash
tiddlywiki mememori --render "[[ToDo]]" "" "text/plain" $:/core/save/all 
d: & cd d:/desktop 
```

!! ''//避免外部程序执行一次，便终止//''
* //''`Call`''// > `call tiddlywiki`
```bash
call tiddlywiki mememori --render "[[ToDo]]" "" "text/plain" $:/core/save/all 
d: & cd d:/desktop 
```






<<list-links "[tag[Binding]]">>












!!//1、Binding：slider -- textblock -- textbox//

```xml
<StackPanel Margin="10">
    <Slider x:Name="slidertextname"/>
    <TextBlock x:Name="textblock" FontSize="{Binding ElementName=slidertextname,Path=Value,Mode=TwoWay}" Content="Simple test"/>
    <TextBox Text="{Binding ElementName=textblock, Path=FontSize,Mode=TwoWay}"/>
</StackPanel>
```
!!//2、`StringFormat='Hello \{0\}'`//

```xml
<!--StringFormat-->
<StackPanel>
    <TextBox x:Name="WelcomeText"/>
    <TextBlock Text="{Binding ElementName=WelcomeText, Path=Text, StringFormat='Hello \{0\}'}" />
</StackPanel>
```

!!//3、和自身 Binding `Mode=Self`//

```xml
<TextBlock Width="200" Text="{Binding Path=Width, RelativeSource={RelativeSource Mode=Self}}" />
```

!!//4、和上级 Binding `Mode=FindAncestor, AncestorType={x:Type StackPanel, AncestorLevel=1`//

!!//1、下拉框 多源属性显示 `DisplayMemberPath SelectedValuePath 为 ItmesControl 的属性`//

* 对于 ComboBox SelectedItem 为 `CombboxItem类`， 属性 `DisplayMemberPath、SelectedValuePath` 表明显示对象为 key 或 Text

!!!//`ComboBox、StackPanel 的 SelectedItem、DataContext = CombboxItem（ComplexInfoModel 类），具有 Key、Text 属性`//

```xml

          DisplayMemberPath="Text" SelectedValuePath="Key" />

<!--注意 DataContext-->

    <TextBlock Text="{Binding Text}"/>
</StackPanel>
```

!!!//在项目开发中，为避免 Class 的变动，导致的 SQL 结构变化，将 Class 采用 Json 封装。类似于 DateTime 封装了 YYYY-MM-DD。采用 `Newtonsoft.Json` 进行序列化（`JsonConvert.SerializeObject`）、反序列化（`JsonConvert.DeserializeObject<RehabWalk>`）//

!!// SQLite 知识回顾 [[C# SQLite]]//

#// 实例化 数据库 类、连接//
#// 读取 Table Name  `SELECT name FROM sqlite_master WHERE TYPE = 'table'`//
#// 读取 Column Name  `cmdtest.CommandText = $"PRAGMA TABLE_INFO({tableSource})";`//
#// 插入数据库  `string.Format(@"INSERT INTO RehabPlan ( id, PatientId ) VALUES ( '{0}', '{1}')", item.Id, item.PatientId)`//
#// 删除数据库  `DELETE FROM RehabPlan`//
#// 查询数据库  `SELECT * FROM RehabPlan`//

!!//1、同一类下，不同实例的 `属性值复制`//
*// propertyClass1 ——> propertyClass0//
*// 获取属性：`PropertyInfo[] myPropertyInfo = propertyClass0.GetType().GetProperties();`//
*// 属性值 复制：`myPropertyInfo[i].SetValue(propertyClass0, myPropertyInfo[i].GetValue(propertyClass1, null), null);`//
*// `GetValue` 和 `SetValue` 方法来自于 `DependencyObject` 类，用于 `获取或设置类的属性值`//

```c
// 将 propertyClass1 属性的值，赋给 propertyClass0
private void BtnInsertproperty_Click(object sender, RoutedEventArgs e)
{
    PropertyClass propertyClass1 = new PropertyClass();
    PropertyClassObject propertyClass0 = new PropertyClassObject();
    propertyClass1.a = "proclass1_a";
    propertyClass1.b = "proclass1_b";
    ……

    //Type t = typeof(PropertyClass);
    PropertyInfo[] myPropertyInfo = propertyClass0.GetType().GetProperties();
    for (int i = 0; i < myPropertyInfo.Length; i++)
    {
        //被赋值对象是 propertyClass0，所赋的值是 i.ToString
        myPropertyInfo[i].SetValue(propertyClass0, myPropertyInfo[i].GetValue(propertyClass1, null), null);
        Console.WriteLine(myPropertyInfo[i].GetValue(propertyClass1, null));
    }
}
```

```c
// 解析json
private void BtnCommit1_Click(object sender, RoutedEventArgs e)
{
    SQLTestConfig();
    RehabWalk rehabWalk = new RehabWalk();
    string jsonInstance = "";
    cmdtest.CommandText = string.Format(@"SELECT Walk FROM RehabPlan WHERE Id = 1");
    crdtest = cmdtest.ExecuteReader();
    while (crdtest.Read())
    {
        jsonInstance = crdtest.GetValue(0).ToString();
    }
    crdtest.Close();
    contest.Close();

    RehabWalk jsonplanid = JsonConvert.DeserializeObject<RehabWalk>(jsonInstance);
    jsonplanid.Walk_Mode = Convert.ToInt32(textboxInsert.Text);
    string jsonnewwalk = JsonConvert.SerializeObject(jsonplanid);
}

!!//LiveCharts不是图形库，更像是代数库。//

* 正常情况下一个图表的呈现过程是这样的：库的核心读取视图中画布的大小，在这种情况下为WPF，然后根据数据在图表中，它计算图表中每个系列，轴或图例所需的每个标签的大小和位置以及形状，最后核心对视图说，嘿！您需要在此处绘制一条线，在此处绘制矩形，并在此处也添加标签。

* 我们可以说该库有2个主要过程，分别是 Calculus 和 Rendering，第一个过程通常非常快，与其他WPF控件一样，遗憾的是，如果使用不正确，则渲染性能很差。

!!//主要内容//
# 使用增强库 ``Geared``，提升 LiveCharts 性能
# 禁用动画 ``DisableAnimations``
# 减少图表中的数值标签 `Hoverable`、`DataTooltip`
# 固定化笔触资源
# 避免 ``.Add()`` 增加子项，采用 ``.AddRange()``

!!//1、使用增强库 ``Geared``，提升 LiveCharts 性能//
!!!`Values = values.AsGearedValues().WithQuality(Quality.Low)`

```c
var series = new GLineSeries
{
    Values = values.AsGearedValues().WithQuality(Quality.Low),
    PointGeometry = null 
    //use a null geometry when you have many series
};
Series.Add(series);
```

!!//2、禁用动画 ``DisableAnimations``//
```xml
<lvc：CartesianChart DisableAnimations="True" />
```

!!//3、减少图表中的数值标签 `Hoverable`、`DataTooltip`//
* ``视觉元素， 截面和 轴的数量应少于25。``
* 尽可能禁用悬停，使用空工具提示并 从图表中删除任何DataClick事件，如果您使用Geared包，则不需要这样做。
```xml
<lvc:CatesianChart Hoverable="False" DataTooltip="{x:Null}" />
```

!!//4、固定化笔触资源//
* 从0.7.15版本开始，默认情况下，默认的笔触，填充和几何形状被冻结。

!!//5、避免 ``.Add()`` 增加子项，采用 ``.AddRange()``//
```c
var temporalCv = new double[1000];

for (var i = 0; i < 1000; i++){
    temporalCv[i] = 5; }
 
var cv = new ChartValues<double>();
cv.AddRange(temporalCv);
 
//or you can also
var cv = temporalCv.AsGearedValues();
```







!!`初始化设置`
```c
public Page3ViewModel()
{
    // 初始化创建一个 X Y 轴上数据显示的图表，并确定 X Y 轴的数据结构
    var mapper = Mappers.Xy<LiveChartsMeasureModel>()
      .X(model => model.DateTime.Ticks)
      .Y(model => model.Value);

    // 配置这个图表，可以被其他地方（特定的方式）使用
    Charting.For<LiveChartsMeasureModel>(mapper);

    // 初始化测量的数据集
    ChartValues = new ChartValues<LiveChartsMeasureModel>();

    // 设置 X 轴显示的标签格式
    DateTimeFormatter = value => new DateTime((long)value).ToString("mm:ss");

    // 设置图表的其他相关属性
    AxisStep = TimeSpan.FromSeconds(1).Ticks;
    AxisUnit = TimeSpan.TicksPerSecond;

    SetAxisLimits(DateTime.Now);  // X 轴上呈现的时间范围

    // 默认情况下开始数据刷新
    IsReading = false;
    this.InjectStopOnClick();
}

// 设置 X 轴上呈现的时间范围
private void SetAxisLimits(DateTime now)
{
    AxisMax = now.Ticks + TimeSpan.FromSeconds(1).Ticks;
    AxisMin = now.Ticks - TimeSpan.FromSeconds(8).Ticks;
}

// 时间格式化器
public Func<double, string> DateTimeFormatter { get; set; }
```

``开始采集数据``

```c
public string ReadingCommandText
{
    get{ return IsReading ? "Stop" : "Start";  }
}

private RelayCommand readingCommand;
public RelayCommand ReadingCommand
{
    get
    {
        if (readingCommand == null)
            readingCommand = new RelayCommand(InjectStopOnClick);
        return readingCommand;
    }
    set { readingCommand = value; }
}

// 根据标识启动采集
public void InjectStopOnClick()
{
    IsReading = !IsReading;
    if (IsReading)
        Task.Factory.StartNew(Read);
    RaisePropertyChanged(nameof(ReadingCommandText));
}

public void Read()
{
    while (IsReading)
    {
        Thread.Sleep(400);
        var now = DateTime.Now;
        double value = Math.Round(new Random().Next(10, 11) + (1 * new Random().NextDouble()), 2);
        ChartValues.Add(new LiveChartsMeasureModel
        {
            DateTime = now,
            Value = value
        });
        SetAxisLimits(now);
        // 只保留160个数据，满了就把前面的数据移除
        if (ChartValues.Count > 160) ChartValues.RemoveAt(0);
    }
    IsReading = false;
}
```

<xmlns:lvc="clr-namespace:LiveCharts.Wpf;assembly=LiveCharts.Wpf">

<lvc:CartesianChart AnimationsSpeed="0:0:0.2" Hoverable="False" DataTooltip="{x:Null}">
    <lvc:CartesianChart.Series>
        <lvc:LineSeries Values="{Binding ChartValues}" PointGeometry="{x:Null}" 
           LineSmoothness="0" StrokeThickness="3" Stroke="#12B1AD" Fill="#E6F7F8"/>
    </lvc:CartesianChart.Series>
    <lvc:CartesianChart.AxisX>
        <lvc:Axis LabelFormatter="{Binding DateTimeFormatter}" MaxValue="{Binding AxisMax}" 
                  MinValue="{Binding AxisMin}" ShowLabels="True" Unit="{Binding AxisUnit}">
            <lvc:Axis.Separator>
                <lvc:Separator Step="{Binding AxisStep}"/>
            </lvc:Axis.Separator>
        </lvc:Axis>
    </lvc:CartesianChart.AxisX>
    <lvc:CartesianChart.AxisY>
        <lvc:Axis ShowLabels="True"/>
    </lvc:CartesianChart.AxisY>
</lvc:CartesianChart>

* //`new RelayCommand(Execute, CanExecute));`//
** 系统首先调用 CanExecute，决定 Button（前端控件）的 IsEnable；实例中 CanTest 返回 true，则 IsEnable = false

```c
private RelayCommand executeCommand;
public RelayCommand ExecuteCommand
{
    get
    {
        return executeCommand ?? (executeCommand = new RelayCommand(DoTest, CanTest));
    }
}

protected virtual void DoTest()
{
    MessageBox.Show("小娴娴");
}

protected virtual bool CanTest()
{
    return true;
}
```

!! //2、''页面切换''：``RelayCommand 继承自 ICommand``//
```c
#region Command - method - 页面切换

private RelayCommand goBackCommand;
public RelayCommand GoBackCommand
{
    get{
        if (goBackCommand == null)
            goBackCommand = new RelayCommand(GoBack);
        return goBackCommand;}
    set { goBackCommand = value; }
}

private void GoBack()
{
    var page = ServiceLocator.Current.GetInstance<INavigationService>();
    page.NavigateTo(CommonKey.Page1Key);
}

#endregion
```

!! //3、''事件转命令''//
!!!文件地址：`pack://application:,,,/Common/Image/beauty1.jpg`

```c
#region 属性 - 事件转命令
private ObservableCollection<Page2Model> listBoxData = new ObservableCollection<Page2Model>()
{
    new Page2Model(){ Img = "pack://application:,,,/Common/Image/beauty1.jpg",  Info="beauty1"},
    new Page2Model(){ Img = "pack://application:,,,/Common/Image/beauty2.jpg",  Info="beauty2"},
    new Page2Model(){ Img = "pack://application:,,,/Common/Image/beauty3.jpg",  Info="beauty3"},
};
public ObservableCollection<Page2Model> ListBoxData
{
    get { return listBoxData; }
    set { listBoxData = value; RaisePropertyChanged(() => listBoxData); }
}
#endregion
```

```c
#region Command - method - 事件转命令

private RelayCommand selectionChangedCommand;
public RelayCommand SelectionChangedCommand
{
    get
    {
        if (selectionChangedCommand == null)
            selectionChangedCommand = new RelayCommand(SelectChange);
        return selectionChangedCommand;
    }
    set { selectionChangedCommand = value; }
}

private void SelectChange()
{
    int i = 0;
    foreach (var item in ListBoxData)
    {
        if (SelectedIndex == i)
            SelectedResult = (item as Page2Model).Info;
            break;
        i++;
    }
}

#endregion
```

```xml
<xmlns:i="http://schemas.microsoft.com/expression/2010/interactivity">

<ListBox x:Name="listBox" ItemsSource="{Binding ListBoxData}" SelectedIndex="{Binding SelectedIndex}">
    <i:Interaction.Triggers>
        <i:EventTrigger EventName="SelectionChanged">
            <i:InvokeCommandAction Command="{Binding SelectionChangedCommand}"/>
        </i:EventTrigger>
    </i:Interaction.Triggers>
    <ListBox.ItemsPanel>
        <ItemsPanelTemplate>
            <WrapPanel Width="{Binding ActualWidth,RelativeSource={RelativeSource AncestorType={x:Type ListBox}}}"/>
        </ItemsPanelTemplate>
    </ListBox.ItemsPanel>
    <ListBox.ItemTemplate>
        <DataTemplate>
            <Border BorderBrush="AntiqueWhite" BorderThickness="1">
                <StackPanel Margin="2">
                    <Image Source="{Binding Img}" Width="230" Height="200"/>
                    <TextBlock Text="{Binding Info}" HorizontalAlignment="Center"/>
                </StackPanel>
            </Border>
        </DataTemplate>
    </ListBox.ItemTemplate>
</ListBox>
```

!!// 4、''拖拽上传''：`本质仍是 事件转命令`//
* 简单拖拽的实现是：
** 源控件的 `MouseDown` 事件，目标控件的 //`Drop`// 事件。
* 调用 `DragDrop.DoDragDrop()` 以启动拖放操作，`DragDrop.DoDragDrop()` 函数接受三个参数：
** `dragSource` 参数。标示了拖拽操作的消息源，所有的消息源事件由谁发出。
** `data` 则用来包装 `Drag&Drop` 所操作的数据。一般情况下，其都是一个 `DataObject` 类型的实例。该实例内部应包装拖拽所实际操作的数据。
** `allowedEffects` 指定拖拽操作的效果

!!! //`DragDrop.DoDragDrop(mListBox, dataObject, DragDropEffects.Copy);`//

# TextBlock AllowDrop = ‘true’
# PassEventArgsToCommand="True"

```xml
<TextBlock Text="拖拽上传" AllowDrop="True" >
    <i:Interaction.Triggers>
        <i:EventTrigger EventName="Drop">
            <mvvm:EventToCommand PassEventArgsToCommand="True" Command="{Binding DropCommand}" />
        </i:EventTrigger>
    </i:Interaction.Triggers>
</TextBlock>
```
!!!//`FileAdd = ((System.Array)e.Data.GetData(System.Windows.DataFormats.FileDrop)).GetValue(0).ToString();`//

```c
 private RelayCommand<DragEventArgs> dropCommand;
 public RelayCommand<DragEventArgs> DropCommand
 {
     get
     {
         if (dropCommand == null)
             dropCommand = new RelayCommand<DragEventArgs>(e => ExecuteDrop(e));
         return dropCommand;
     }
     set { dropCommand = value; }
 }
 private void ExecuteDrop(DragEventArgs e)
 {
     FileAdd = ((System.Array)e.Data.GetData(System.Windows.DataFormats.FileDrop)).GetValue(0).ToString();
 }
```


!!// 5、''单参数命令绑定''：``Func<string, bool>有疑问，bool isCanAddUser 用于 AddUser 是否可用``//
* 若不考虑 IsCanAddUser，采用  `addUserCommand = new RelayCommand<string>((p) => AddUser(p));`

```c
#region Command - method - 单参数命令绑定

private RelayCommand<string> addUserCommand;
public RelayCommand<string> AddUserCommand
{
    get
    {
        if (addUserCommand == null)
            addUserCommand = new RelayCommand<string>(AddUser, (string p) => { return IsCanAddUser; });
            // 若不考虑 IsCanAddUser，采用如下
            addUserCommand = new RelayCommand<string>((p) => AddUser(p));
        return addUserCommand;
    }
    set { addUserCommand = value; }
}

private void AddUser(string par)
{
    UserList = UserList + " " + par;
}

#endregion
```
```xml
<Button Command="{Binding AddUserCommand}" 
        CommandParameter="{Binding ElementName=tbUser, Path=Text}" 
        IsEnabled="{Binding IsCanAddUser}"/>
```

!!// 6、''多参数命令绑定''//
* 或直接再 View 中 传递 一个 Model 类
```xml
<xmlns:model="clr-namespace:MVVMLightDemo.Model">

<Button.CommandParameter>
    <model:CustomClass Age="15" >
</Button.CommandParameter>
```

```c
#region Command - method - 多参数命令绑定

private RelayCommand<Page2ViewModel> addUserCommandWithObjPar;
public RelayCommand<Page2ViewModel> ADDUserCommandWithObjPar
{
    get
    {
        if (addUserCommandWithObjPar == null)
            addUserCommandWithObjPar = new RelayCommand<Page2ViewModel>(AddUserWithObjPar);
        return addUserCommandWithObjPar; }
    set { addUserCommandWithObjPar = value; }
}

private void AddUserWithObjPar(Page2ViewModel par)
{
    ObjParaMeter = "UserName: " + par.UserName + "; Password: " + par.PassWord;
}

#endregion
```

```c
public class UserInfoConverter : IMultiValueConverter
{
    public object Convert(object[] values, Type targetType, object parameter, CultureInfo culture)
    {
        if (!values.Cast<string>().Any(text => string.IsNullOrEmpty(text)) && values.Count() == 2)
            Page2ViewModel userModel = new Page2ViewModel()
            {
                UserName = values[0].ToString(),
                PassWord = values[1].ToString(),
            };
            return userModel;
        return null;
    }

    public object[] ConvertBack(object value, Type[] targetTypes, object parameter, CultureInfo culture)
    {
        throw new NotImplementedException();
    }
}
```

```xml
<xmlns:cvt="clr-namespace:MVVMDemo.View.Converter">

<Page.Resources>
    <cvt:UserInfoConverter x:Key="userInfoConverter"/>
</Page.Resources>

<Button Command="{Binding ADDUserCommandWithObjPar}">
    <Button.CommandParameter>
        <MultiBinding Converter="{StaticResource userInfoConverter}">
            <Binding ElementName="tbxUser" Path="Text"/>
            <Binding ElementName="tbxPwd" Path="Text"/>
        </MultiBinding>
    </Button.CommandParameter>
</Button>

!!MVVMLight 用于解耦 view、model 和 viewModel

NuGet添加MVVMLight类库，自动创建了MainViewModel.cs 和 ViewModelLocator.cs文件，App.xaml文件中，将ViewModelLocator作为资源添加至Application.Resources

```xml
<Application.Resources>
   <ResourceDictionary>
      <vm:ViewModelLocator x:Key="Locator" d:IsDataSource="True" xmlns:vm="clr-namespace:HelloMvvmLight.ViewModel" />
   </ResourceDictionary>
</Application.Resources>
```

''传统数据绑定''：
``对应 Window 的 xaml 或 cs 文件中 new ViewModel 实例，通过 DataContext 绑定``

''MVVMLight中''：``ViewModelLocator 类用于创建实例，SimpleIoc 简单的依赖注入容器，注入 服务 或 类、ViewModel``

```c
public class ViewModelLocator
{
   /// Initializes a new instance of the ViewModelLocator class.
   public ViewModelLocator()
   {
      ServiceLocator.SetLocatorProvider(() => SimpleIoc.Default);
      // MainViewModel 需要实现的服务，例：需要 Person类
      SimpleIoc.Default.Register<Person>(()=>new Person());
      //将 MainViewModel 注册到 SimpleIoc
      SimpleIoc.Default.Register<MainViewModel>();
   }
   //通过 Main 属性获取 MainViewModel 实例
   public MainViewModel Main
   {
      get{return ServiceLocator.Current.GetInstance<MainViewModel>();}
   }
        
   public static void Cleanup()
   {
      // TODO Clear the ViewModels
   }
}
```

App.xaml 中 ViewModelLocator 实例资源，在XAML中以 StaticResource key形式获取

```xml
<Window.DataContext>
   <Binding Path="Main" Source="{StaticResource Locator}"/>
</Window.DataContext>
```

''为什么使用ViewModelLocator？''

* View 和 ViewModel 之间不直接引用，通过 ViewModelLocator 关联
* ViewModelLocator 中的 ViewModel 为 单例，全局引用绑定
*避免频繁创建 ViewModel，资源释放出错，导致的内存泄露

''Command 的绑定？''

```c
public class MainViewModel : ViewModelBase
{
   private string title;
   public string Title
   {
       get { return title; }
       set { Set(ref title , value); }
   }
   
   public ICommand ChangeTitleCommand { get; set; }

   /// Initializes a new instance of the MainViewModel class.
   public MainViewModel()
   {
       Title = "Hello World";
       ChangeTitleCommand = new RelayCommand(ChangeTitle);
   }
   // 匹配 Person 类，先前 ViewModelLocator 已注册
   private void ChangeTitle( Person data )
   {
       Title = "Hello MvvmLight";
       Name = data.Name
   }
}
```

```xml
<Window x:Class="HelloMvvmLight.MainWindow"
        xmlns:local="clr-namespace:HelloMvvmLight">
    <Window.DataContext>
        <Binding Path="Main" Source="{StaticResource Locator}"/>
    </Window.DataContext>
    <Grid>
        <TextBlock Text="{Binding Title}"></TextBlock>
        <Button Command="{Binding ChangeTitleCommand}"></Button>
    </Grid>
</Window>
```

``RelayCommand类，继承自 ICommand 接口，可直接 xaml 中绑定；ViewModelBase 继承了 INotifyPropertyChanged 接口，并提供 Set 方法为属性赋值，也可手动通知 RaisePropertyChanged``







!!MVVMLight 中的 INavigationService 接口，实现对 导航 的支持

``新建 PageTwoViewModel ，自动获取实例 navigationService``

!!//为什么 PageTwoViewModel 的构造函数参数中带有 INavigationService，即可由 IOC 自动获取实例 navigationService ?//

```c
public class PageTwoViewModel
{
   private INavigationService _navigationService;
   
   public ICommand GoBackCommand { get; set; }
   
   public PageTwoViewModel(INavigationService navigationService)
   {
       _navigationService = navigationService;
       GoBackCommand = new RelayCommand(()=> { _navigationService.GoBack(); });
   }
}
```

``INavigationService 具有如下方法``

```c
public interface INavigationService
{
    string CurrentPageKey { get; }
    void GoBack();
    void NavigateTo(string pageKey);
    void NavigateTo(string pageKey, object parameter);
}
```

``创建 INavigationService 实例，关联各个 Page``

```c
public ViewModelLocator()
{
    ServiceLocator.SetLocatorProvider(() => SimpleIoc.Default);
    SimpleIoc.Default.Register<MainViewModel>();
    SimpleIoc.Default.Register<PageTwoViewModel>();

    var navigationService = this.CreateNavigationService();
    SimpleIoc.Default.Register<INavigationService>(() => navigationService);
}

private INavigationService CreateNavigationService()
{
    var navigationService = new NavigationService();
    navigationService.Configure("MainPage", typeof(MainPage));
    navigationService.Configure("PageTwo", typeof(PageTwo));

    return navigationService;
}
```

``修改 MainViewModel，手动获取 navigationService 对象``

```c
public MainViewModel()
{
    Title = "Hello World";
    ChangeTitleCommand = new RelayCommand(ChangeTitle);
    GotoNextCommand = new RelayCommand(GotoNext);
}

private void GotoNext()
{
    var navigationService = ServiceLocator.Current.GetInstance<INavigationService>();
    navigationService.NavigateTo("PageTwo");
}

private void ChangeTitle()
{
    Title = "Hello MvvmLight";
}
```

!!//10、更改Table值，实时更新（`该案例貌似 有问题，无法智能化，只能根据 row、column位置进行传递参数`）//
```c
private void Btnread_Click(object sender, RoutedEventArgs e)
{
    connection();
    string query1 = @"select * from Users";
    SQLiteCommand cmd = new SQLiteCommand(query1, con);
    SQLiteDataAdapter dataAdapter = new SQLiteDataAdapter(cmd);
    DataSet ds = new DataSet();
    dataAdapter.Fill(ds, "Users");
    DataView dv = new DataView(ds.Tables["Users"]);
    datagrid.ItemsSource = dv;
    crd.Close();
}

// 数据库文件的更新
public void submitData()
{
    DataTable dt = (datagrid.ItemsSource as DataView).Table;

    string query1 = @"select * from Users";
    SQLiteConnection conn = new SQLiteConnection(query1);
    SQLiteDataAdapter dta = new SQLiteDataAdapter(cmd);
    SQLiteCommandBuilder cb = new SQLiteCommandBuilder(dta);
    cb.RefreshSchema();
    dta.Update(dt);
}
```







!!! //`DragDrop.DoDragDrop(mListBox, dataObject, DragDropEffects.Copy);`//
* 简单拖拽的实现是：
** 源控件的 `MouseDown` 事件，目标控件的 //`Drop`// 事件。
* 调用 `DragDrop.DoDragDrop()` 以启动拖放操作，`DragDrop.DoDragDrop()` 函数接受三个参数：
** `dragSource` 参数。标示了拖拽操作的消息源，所有的消息源事件由谁发出。
** `data` 则用来包装 `Drag&Drop` 所操作的数据。一般情况下，其都是一个 `DataObject` 类型的实例。该实例内部应包装拖拽所实际操作的数据。
** `allowedEffects` 指定拖拽操作的效果

!!//1、从 GroupBox 中拖拽 TextBox 至右侧 ListBox//
* 数据源 //`MouseDown`//；
** `(TextBlock)e.OriginalSource`
** //`DragDrop.DoDragDrop(obj, obj.Text, DragDropEffects.Copy);`//
* 目的地 //`Drop`//
** //`e.Data.GetData(DataFormats.Text).ToString();`//

```xml
<!--数据源-->
<GroupBox x:Name="groupBox" Header="GroupBox" MouseDown="TextBlock_MouseDown">
	<StackPanel Margin="10">
		<TextBlock>足球</TextBlock>
		<TextBlock>篮球</TextBlock>
	</StackPanel>
</GroupBox>
<!--目的地-->
<ListBox x:Name="listBox" Drop="listBox_Drop" AllowDrop="True"/>
```

```c
private void TextBlock_MouseDown(object sender, MouseButtonEventArgs e)
{
    TextBlock obj = (TextBlock)e.OriginalSource;
    DragDrop.DoDragDrop(obj, obj.Text, DragDropEffects.Copy);
}

private void listBox_Drop(object sender, DragEventArgs e)
{
    string data = e.Data.GetData(DataFormats.Text).ToString();
    listBox.Items.Add(data);
}
```

!!//2、拖拽文件夹，获取文件夹下所有文件//
!!// 先验知识：////[[C# 文件(夹)操作]]//
* //`((Array)e.Data.GetData(DataFormats.FileDrop)).GetValue(0).ToString();`//
* //`var item in Directory.GetFiles(floder)`//
* //`listBox.Items.Add(item);`//

```xml
<Grid Drop="textBox_Drop">
	<!--输入 文件夹路径-->
	<TextBlock x:Name="txtfloder" Drop="listBox_Drop" AllowDrop="True"/>
	<!--返回值：文件夹下，所有文件-->
	<ListBox x:Name="listBox"/>
</Grid>
```

```c
private void textBox_Drop(object sender, DragEventArgs e)
{
    if (e.Data.GetDataPresent(DataFormats.FileDrop))
        listBox.Items.Clear();
        string floder = ((Array)e.Data.GetData(DataFormats.FileDrop)).GetValue(0).ToString();
        if (Directory.Exists(floder))
        {
            txtfloder.Text = floder.ToString();
            foreach (var item in Directory.GetFiles(floder))
            {
                listBox.Items.Add(item);
            }
            foreach (var item in Directory.GetFiles(floder))
            {
                fileList.Items.Add(item);
            }
        }
        else
            txtfloder.Text = "无效文件夹";
}
```







!! 主函数 调用 另一个非静态函数，提示：//`对象对于引用非静态对象、方法或属性是必需的`//
---
!!!//错误提示翻译：//
!!//`非静态`对象、方法、属性 需要 `对象`//

!!!//解决方案：//
* 非静态方法 ——> //`static`//，以便能被 `非静态方法` 调用
* `对象` ，即 //`实例化`//，通过`实例化的对象`进行调用

---
!!//__总结：__//

!!//类中`静态方法`不能访问 `非静态成员`//
!!//`static`修饰的函数或变量都是在`类初始化`的时候加载的，而 `非静态`的变量都是在`对象初始化`的时候加载。//
* `static`修饰的对象，只能通过 `类名`调用

!!//1、IDataErrorInfo//
* 继承自 IDataErrorInfo
* RegularExpressions 验证
** //`Regex digitalReg = new Regex(@"^[-]?[1-9]{8,11}\d*$|^[0]{1}$");`//
** //`String.IsNullOrEmpty(this.UserName))`//
** //`!digitalReg.IsMatch(this.UserPhone.ToString()))`//
* `ValidatesOnDataErrors=True`


```c
using System.Text.RegularExpressions;

public class BindingFormViewModel : ViewModelBase, IDataErrorInfo
{
    public String this[string columnName]
    {
        get
        {
            Regex digitalReg = new Regex(@"^[-]?[1-9]{8,11}\d*$|^[0]{1}$");
            Regex emailReg = new Regex("^\\s*([A-Za-z0-9_-]+(\\.\\w+)*@(\\w+\\.)+\\w{2,5})\\s*$");
    
            if (columnName == "UserName" && String.IsNullOrEmpty(this.UserName))
                return "用户名不能为空";    
            if (columnName == "UserPhone" && !digitalReg.IsMatch(this.UserPhone.ToString()))
                return "用户电话必须为8-11位的数值！";    
            if (columnName == "UserEmail" && !emailReg.IsMatch(this.UserEmail.ToString()))
                return "用户邮箱地址不正确！";    
            return null;
        }
    }
}
```

```xml
<!--ValidatesOnDataErrors=True-->

<TextBox x:Name="UserName" Text="{Binding UserName, Mode=TwoWay, UpdateSourceTrigger=PropertyChanged, ValidatesOnDataErrors=True}" />
<TextBox x:Name="UserPhone" Text="{Binding UserPhone, Mode=TwoWay, UpdateSourceTrigger=PropertyChanged, ValidatesOnDataErrors=True}" />
<TextBox x:Name="UserEmail" Text="{Binding UserEmail, Mode=TwoWay, UpdateSourceTrigger=PropertyChanged, ValidatesOnDataErrors=True}" />
```

!!//2、ValidationRule//
* // Regex 汉字匹配 `^[\u4e00-\u9fa5]{2,4}$`//
* // `ValidatesOnDataErrors=True`//

```c
public class NameRule : ValidationRule
{
    public override ValidationResult Validate(object value, CultureInfo cultureInfo)
    {
        Regex nameReg = new Regex("^[\\u4e00-\\u9fa5]{2,4}$");
        if (value == null)
            return new ValidationResult(false,"姓名不能为空！");
        if (!string.IsNullOrEmpty(value.ToString()))
            if (!nameReg.IsMatch(value.ToString()))
                return new ValidationResult(false, "请输入有效姓名！");
        return new ValidationResult(true, null);
    }
}
```
```xml
<!--NameRule-->
<!--ValidatesOnDataErrors=True-->
<TextBox>
    <TextBox.Text>
        <Binding Path="Name" ValidatesOnDataErrors="True">
            <Binding.ValidationRules>
                <ValidationRules: NameRule/>
            </Binding.ValidationRules>
        </Binding>
    </TextBox.Text>
</TextBox>
```


!!//3、throw Exception 简单粗暴，`属性`//
```c
// 姓名 Name
private string _name;
public string Name
{
    get { return _name; }
    set
    {
        int ch = 0;    // 统计汉字的个数
        char[] array = value.ToCharArray();   // 将字符串转化为数组
        foreach (var item in array)
        {
            if (item == ' ')
                throw new Exception("姓名中不得出现空格");
            else
                ch += 1;
        }
        if (ch > 4 || ch < 2)
            throw new Exception("请输入正确姓名");

        _name = value;
    }
}
```







!!//1、IDataErrorInfo//

```c
public class NameRule : ValidationRule
{
    public override ValidationResult Validate(object value, CultureInfo cultureInfo)
    {
        Regex nameReg = new Regex("^[\\u4e00-\\u9fa5]{2,4}$");
        if (value == null)
            return new ValidationResult(false,"姓名不能为空！");
        if (!string.IsNullOrEmpty(value.ToString()))
            if (!nameReg.IsMatch(value.ToString()))
                return new ValidationResult(false, "请输入有效姓名！");
        return new ValidationResult(true, null);
    }
}
```
```xml
<!--NameRule-->
<!--ValidatesOnDataErrors=True-->
<TextBox>
    <TextBox.Text>
        <Binding Path="Name" ValidatesOnDataErrors="True">
            <Binding.ValidationRules>
                <ValidationRules: NameRule/>
            </Binding.ValidationRules>
        </Binding>
    </TextBox.Text>
</TextBox>
```


!!//3、throw Exception 简单粗暴，`属性`//
```c
// 姓名 Name
private string _name;
public string Name
{
    get { return _name; }
    set
    {
        int ch = 0;    // 统计汉字的个数
        char[] array = value.ToCharArray();   // 将字符串转化为数组
        foreach (var item in array)
        {
            if (item == ' ')
                throw new Exception("姓名中不得出现空格");
            else
                ch += 1;
        }
        if (ch > 4 || ch < 2)
            throw new Exception("请输入正确姓名");

        _name = value;
    }
}
```

!! //先验知识：////[[C# 文件(夹)操作]]//
# 移动文件
# 读取文件，拆分标记
# 合并 txt 文档

!!//1、文件移动 任务描述//
*筛选信息：待移动文件的文件名，存储地址`string selectedPath = @"D:\Desktop\beauty.txt";`
*待筛选文件：`string path = @"D:\Desktop\LUXU";`
*目标地址：`string desPath = @"D:\Desktop\Beauty";`

```c
DirectoryInfo root = new DirectoryInfo(path);
FileInfo[] fileInfos = root.GetFiles();

//读取txt，存入list，查找文件名相符合元素，移动至目标文件夹
private static void FileSelected(FileInfo[] fileInfos, string selectedPath, string desPath)
{
	//fileInfos 待筛选文件
	//selectedPath txt文件地址，存储待筛选文件名
	//desPath  移动目标地址
    try
    {
        List<string> fileName = new List<string>();
        foreach (var item in fileInfos)
        {
            fileName.Add(item.Name);  // 文件名
        }

        string[] fileS = File.ReadAllLines(selectedPath, Encoding.Default);
        int fileIndexPre = 0;
        foreach (var item in fileS)
        {
            for (int i = fileIndexPre; i < fileInfos.Length; i++)
            {
                if (fileInfos[i].Name.ToString().Contains(item))
                    fileInfos[i].MoveTo(Path.Combine(desPath, fileInfos[i].Name));
                    fileIndexPre = i;
            }
        }
    }
    catch (System.Exception e)
    {
        System.Console.WriteLine(e.Message);
        throw;
    }
}
```

!!//3、txt 合并，注意 `Encoding`//
```c
# region 读文件，注意 Encoding
List<string> chapter = new List<string>();
foreach (var item in fileInfos)
{              
    using(StreamReader streamReader = new StreamReader(item.FullName, Encoding.Default))
    {
        while (streamReader.Peek() > -1)
        {
            chapter.Add(streamReader.ReadToEnd());
        }
        chapter.Add("newChapter");  // 拆分标记
    }
}
# endregion

# region 写文件，注意 Encoding
using (StreamWriter streamWriter = new StreamWriter(destination, false, Encoding.UTF8))
{
    foreach (var item in chapter)
    {
        streamWriter.WriteLine(item);
    }
}
# endregion
```









!!//开机自启动实现方式（注册表）：//
# 安装包设置
# 后台代码实现

!!//1、安装包设置//
<<<
!!// [[VS打包安装程序]]//
<<<

* SetUp Project > View > 注册表
* 添加字段至 HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE（所有用户）
**`\HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SOFTWARE\WOW6432Node\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\Run` (win10_64)
** `\HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\Run` (win7_64)
** Name：自定义
** Value：`"[TARGETDIR]xxx.exe" /background`（软件物理路径）
*** `[TARGETDIR]` 获取用户安装路径
***`xxx.exe`为 `主程序名（软件的启动文件名）`

!!//2、[[后台代码实现|https://www.cnblogs.com/henryzong/p/6209797.html?utm_source=itdadao&utm_medium=referral]]//
*//CMD 查看注册表：`regedit`//
*//设置注册表：`myReg.SetValue(shortFileName, fileName);`//
*//删除注册表：`myReg.DeleteValue(shortFileName, false);`//

```c
private void RunAtStart()
{
    var starupPath = GetType().Assembly.Location;
    try
    {
        var fileName = starupPath;
        var shortFileName = fileName.Substring(fileName.LastIndexOf('\\') + 1);
        //打开子键节点
        var myReg = Registry.LocalMachine.OpenSubKey(
            "SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Windows\\CurrentVersion\\Run", RegistryKeyPermissionCheck.ReadWriteSubTree,
            RegistryRights.FullControl);
        if (myReg == null)
        {
            //如果子键节点不存在，则创建之
            myReg = Registry.LocalMachine.CreateSubKey("SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Windows\\CurrentVersion\\Run");
        }
        if (myReg != null && myReg.GetValue(shortFileName) != null)
        {
            //在注册表中设置自启动程序
            myReg.DeleteValue(shortFileName);
            myReg.SetValue(shortFileName, fileName);
            Console.WriteLine("设置自启动程序操作成功");
        }
        else if (myReg != null && myReg.GetValue(shortFileName) == null)
        {
            myReg.SetValue(shortFileName, fileName);
            Console.WriteLine("设置自启动程序操作成功");
        }
    }
    catch
    {
        Console.WriteLine("写注册表操作发生错误");
    }
}
```

```c
public class ToMultiRatio : IMultiValueConverter
{
    public object Convert(object[] values, Type targetType, object parameter, CultureInfo culture)
    {
        double gridwidth = double.Parse(values[0].ToString());
        double cellwidth = double.Parse(values[1].ToString());
        double time = Math.Round(cellwidth / gridwidth * 30);
        string dtime = string.Format("{0:F0}min", time);
        return (dtime);
    }
    …………
}
```

!!//1、获取初始化系统亮度//
```c
static int GetBrightness()
{
    ManagementScope scope = new ManagementScope("root\\WMI");
    SelectQuery query = new SelectQuery("WmiMonitorBrightness");
    using (ManagementObjectSearcher searcher = new ManagementObjectSearcher(scope, query))
    {
        using (ManagementObjectCollection objectCollection = searcher.Get())
        {
            foreach (ManagementObject mObj in objectCollection)
            {
                var br_obj = mObj.Properties["CurrentBrightness"].Value;

                int br = 0;
                int.TryParse(br_obj + "", out br);
                return br;
                //break;
            }
        }
    }
    return 0;
}
```

!!//2、设置系统亮度//
```c
static void SetBrightness(byte targetBrightness)
{
    ManagementScope scope = new ManagementScope("root\\WMI");
    SelectQuery query = new SelectQuery("WmiMonitorBrightnessMethods");
    using (ManagementObjectSearcher searcher = new ManagementObjectSearcher(scope, query))
    {
        using (ManagementObjectCollection objectCollection = searcher.Get())
        {
            foreach (ManagementObject mObj in objectCollection)
            {
                mObj.InvokeMethod("WmiSetBrightness",
                    new Object[] { UInt32.MaxValue, targetBrightness });
                break;
            }
        }
    }
}
```

```c
public class Battery : Control
{
    static Battery()
    {
        DefaultStyleKeyProperty.OverrideMetadata(typeof(Battery), new FrameworkPropertyMetadata(typeof(Battery)));
    }

    public double Value
    {
        get { return (double)GetValue(ValueProperty); }
        set { SetValue(ValueProperty, value); }
    }

    public static readonly DependencyProperty ValueProperty =
        DependencyProperty.Register("Value", typeof(double), typeof(Battery));


    public Brushes BorderBrushes
    {
        get { return (Brushes)GetValue(BorderBrushesProperty); }
        set { SetValue(BorderBrushesProperty, value); }
    }

    public static readonly DependencyProperty BorderBrushesProperty =
        DependencyProperty.Register("BorderBrushes", typeof(Brushes), typeof(Battery));
}
```

```c
#region -- 值转换器 -- 不同颜色表达相应 电量值
public class BrushesConverter : IValueConverter
{
    public object Convert(object value, Type targetType, object parameter, CultureInfo culture)
    {
        if ((double)value > 0.8)
            return Brushes.LightGreen;
        else if ((double)value > 0.2)
            return Brushes.Yellow;
        else
            return Brushes.Red;
    }
    …………
}
#endregion

#region -- 值转换器 -- 电量值转换相应 height
public class HeightConverter : IMultiValueConverter
{
    public object Convert(object[] values, Type targetType, object parameter, CultureInfo culture)
    {
        Grid grid = (Grid)values[0];
        double value = (double)values[1];
        return grid.ColumnDefinitions[0].ActualWidth * value;
    }
    …………
}
#endregion

                            <RowDefinition/>

!!//1、初始化系统音量//
```c
using CoreAudioApi;

MMDeviceEnumerator devices = new MMDeviceEnumerator();
device = devices.GetDefaultAudioEndpoint(EDataFlow.eRender, ERole.eMultimedia);
RbtnMute.IsChecked = IsMute;
```

!!//2、系统音量设置//
```c
public int CurrentVolume
{
    get => Convert.ToInt32(device.AudioEndpointVolume.MasterVolumeLevelScalar * 100.0f);
}

public int SetVolume
{
    get => CurrentVolume;
    set
    {
        if (value < 0) device.AudioEndpointVolume.MasterVolumeLevelScalar = 0.0f;
        else if (value > 100) device.AudioEndpointVolume.MasterVolumeLevelScalar = 100.0f;
        else device.AudioEndpointVolume.MasterVolumeLevelScalar = value / 100.0f;
    }
}

public bool IsMute
{
    get { return device.AudioEndpointVolume.Mute; }
    set { device.AudioEndpointVolume.Mute = value; }
}
```

!! //~ViewModelMonitor.cs//

* 1392-1426行 属性 `RecipeTimeDelay  RecipeTimeScale  RecipeCssSetValue2`
* 1113行 修改了 `SelectRecipeCommand 的 DoSelectRecipe()、CanSelectRecipe()`
** 这个地方错的，没有改，延时放在了 ~CanSelectRecipe()这边（X）

!! //~ViewModelMain.cs//
* //''主~ViewModel''//
* //''修改目的：每 6秒读取 ~RunningTime[9]，判断是否处于带负载状态，`记录带负载运作时间 + 运转初始CSS`''//
* 772行 + 777-782行 定时器 `private System.Threading.Timer timerLoadCss;`，//''该定时器没有 Dispose''//
* 属性 `loadTime、cssStart`
* 801-833 定时器回调函数
** 连续3次 `RunningTime[9] > 阈值(自定义为 1000)`，记为开始带负载状态，记录timeStart、cssStart
** 连续3次 `RunningTime[9](List末尾) < 阈值/5`，记为结束带负载状态，记录timeStop、cssStop
** 计算带负载时间，`timeStop - timeStart`，转为h；`累加至 loadTime`；
** 循环

!! //~ViewModelCalibration.cs//
* //''~CalibrationDetail.xaml 对应 ~ViewModel''//
* 386-387行 实例化类 `ViewModelMain、ViewModelMonitor`
* 391行 ~DoNext() 进行 xmlCalibration 的创建、写入//''`SaveCalibration()`''//和计算每小时补偿值//''`ReadCalibration()`''//
* 414行 定时器回调函数 //''`timerCalibrationPerHourCallBack()`''//，进行补偿

!! //XML文件结构//
```xml
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<Calibration Description="Time and Value to record Calibration">
  <CalibrationItem Time="0" Value="100" />
  <CalibrationItem Time="100" Value="300" />
  <CalibrationItem Time="50" Value="400" />
  ……
</Calibration>
```
* Time值：带负载运行的时长，小时计；Value值：CSS值
* 第一个元素`<CalibrationItem Time="0" Value="100" />`
** 带负载运行的初始值，Time：时长为0；初始CSS值为：100
* 第二个元素`<CalibrationItem Time="100" Value="300" />`
** 表示首次运行 ~ 第一次标定，带负载运行时间为：100h；标定的CSS值为 300
* ……

* Base.xml 内容，貌似自动创建
* Base - eng.xml，貌似需手动添加






!! ''//[[CIS修改记录_6.1]]//''

!! ''//~ViewModelMonitor.cs//''
* 主要用于 //''~MultiCss''//，//''`不清楚总工作时间，时间比例就显得没意义`''//，目前按照//''`一小时`''//计算
* //''~ProgramWindow.xaml 对应 ~ViewModel''//

!! ''//~ViewModelMain.cs//''
* //''主~ViewModel''//
* 带负载工作时间的累加，通过直接读取//''`RunningTime[9]`''//

!! ''//~ViewModelCalibration.cs//''
* //''~CalibrationDetail.xaml 对应 ~ViewModel''//
* 默认：//''标定是最频繁的操纵''//，相对于：衬板更换、复位
* //''需要避免带负载工作时间过短''//

! ''//CISCalibrationDemo//''
* 带负载时间，每10s累加10；
* 设定每10s，自动补偿
* 点击CSS标定Button，xml文件写入`LoadTime`、`Value`、`Time`，开始自动补偿（自动补偿，需要连续标定2次已上）
* 若两次标定之间时间间隔过短（<20s），视为标定值的更新
* 为避免带负载工作时间过短（<40s），造成的单位时间补偿值过大，删除上一次标定值，更新带负载时间、CSS标定值


!! ''//XML文件结构//''
```xml
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<Calibration>
  <CalibrationSetting>
    <CalibrationTimeUnit CalibrationTime="60" />
  </CalibrationSetting>
  <CalibrationTimeValue Description="Time and Value to record Calibration">
    <CalibrationItem LoadTime="1.2" Value="100" Time=“2020/6/14 12:57:12”/>
  </CalibrationTimeValue>
</Calibration>
```

切换至目标盘符：输入``D:``；切换至  ``D:\>``

切换至目标盘符下文件夹：输入``cd D:\Temp``，切换至目标文件夹

* 需处于 `目标盘符下`

返回上层文件夹：输入``cd..``

进入下一级文件夹 xxx：输入`cd ./xxx`







!!//[[CMD]] 多命令组合// 
* &，同时执行两个命令
* |，上一个输出，作为下一个输入
* &&，当前命令执行成功后，方可执行之后命令
* ||，失败时，才执行

```bash
d:&cd d:/temp&.\youtube-dl https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1Zk4y197QB
```

!!//返回值：`Day.HH:mm:ss`//

```c
string dt1 = "2016/06/23 10:20:30";
string dt2 = "2013/06/24 00:00:0";
DateTime t1 = toDateTime2(dt1);
DateTime t2 = toDateTime2(dt2);
//返回值：Day.HH:mm:ss
TimeSpan diff = t1 - t2;
```

!!//[[FFmpeg]]：Fast Forward Moving Picture Experts Group//
!!//A complete, cross-platform solution to record, convert and stream audio and video. //
<<<

!//不常用功能代码：//
* 帮助文档：`fmpeg -h`
* 播放音视频：`ffplay xian.mp4`、`ffplay xian.acc`
** `Q`、`Esc`：退出播放
** `键盘方向键`、`鼠标右键`：播放进度
** `P`、`Space`：暂停
** `F`：全屏
** `W`：切换显示模式
* 查看媒体信息：`ffprobe xian.mp4`
** 媒体参数 + 视频流参数 + 音频流参数
* 查看编码器、解码器：`ffmpeg -codecs`
* 截图(第5秒第1帧)：`ffmpeg -i input.mp4 -ss 5 -vframes 1 img.jpg`
** `-vframes`：关键帧
* 水印：`ffmpeg -i video.mp4 -i qt.png -filter_complex "overlay=20:80" video_watermark.mp4`
** `-filter_complex`：添加滤镜；`"overlay=20:80"`：Margin_Left：20，Margin_Up：80








<<<
!!//[[FFmpeg]]：Fast Forward Moving Picture Experts Group//
!!//A complete, cross-platform solution to record, convert and stream audio and video. //
<<<

!!//1、Concat协议进行视频文件合并//
* `MPEG`格式文件，直接合并，尺寸需一致
** `ffmpeg -i concat:"1.mpg|2.mpg|3.mpg" -c copy output.mp4`
* 非MPEG格式文件，MPEG编码器，转换为TS格式容器，尺寸可不一致
** `ffmpeg -i 1.mp4 -c copy -bsf:v h264_mp4toannexb -f mpegts 1.ts`

!!//2、Concat分离器（优）//
* //可合并不同尺寸，不可合并不同格式//
* 创建文件`fileList.txt`
** file 'input1.mkv'<br>file 'input2.mkv'<br>file 'input3.mkv'
* `ffmpeg -f concat -i filelist.txt -c copy output.mkv`

!!//3、Concat滤镜(filter，有损)//
* //可合并不同格式，不可合并不同尺寸//
* `ffmpeg -i 1.mp4 -i 2.mp4 -i 3.mp4 -filter_complex '[0:0] [0:1] [1:0] [1:1] [2:0] [2:1] concat=n=3:v=1:a=1 [v] [a]' -map '[v]' -map '[a]’  output.mp4`
** `[0:0] [0:1] [1:0] [1:1] [2:0] [2:1]`：第一个输入文件的视频、音频、第二个输入文件的视频、音频、第三个输入文件的视频、音频
** `concat=n=3:v=1:a=1`：有三个输入文件，输出一条视频流和一条音频流






<<<
!!//[[FFmpeg]]：Fast Forward Moving Picture Experts Group//
!!//A complete, cross-platform solution to record, convert and stream audio and video. //
<<<

!//FFmpeg常用 CMD参数：//
!!//1、主要命令：//
* `-i` //(input)//设定输入流，文件名不得有空格
* `-f` 设定输出格式 
* `-ss` 开始时间
* `-to` 结束时间

!!//2、视频参数：//
* `-b` //(bit rate)//，设定视频流量(码率)，默认//200Kbit/s//，`不推荐`
* `-r` //(rate)//，设定帧速率，默认//25// 
* `-s` 设定画面的宽与高 
* `-aspect` 设定画面的比例 
* `-vn` 不处理视频 
* `-vcodec` //(Vidoe Coder Decoder)//，设定视频编解码器，未设定时则使用与输入流相同的编解码器 
* `-qscale` 动态码率，值4、6，`-qscale 6`较好，体积较`-b`好
* `-preset` 编码器预设，默认`medium`，录屏`veryfast`，压制`veryslow`
* `-profile` 编码器配置，和`压缩比`有关；实时通信`-baseline`，流媒体`-main`，超清视频`-high`
* `-level:v` 对编码器设置的具体规范和限制，权衡压缩比和画质；正常1080P选择`4.1`，720P选择`4`
* `-crf` //(const rate factor)//码率控制模式，适用`高画质，忽略尺寸`，默认23

!!//3、音频参数//
* `-ab` 码率，默认//128k//
* `-ar` 设定采样率，默认原始采样率
* `-ac` 设定声音的Channel数，默认原始
* `-acodec` //(Audio Coder Decoder)//，设定声音编解码器，未设定时则与输入流相同编解码器，`libmp3lame`、`acc`
* `-an` 不处理音频






<<<
!!//[[FFmpeg]]：Fast Forward Moving Picture Experts Group//
!!//A complete, cross-platform solution to record, convert and stream audio and video. //
<<<

!//常用功能(转码、剪切、合并、倍速)：//
!!//1、转码（视频容器转换）：//
* `ffmpeg -i input.avi output.mp4`
* `ffmpeg -i out.ogv -vcodec h264 out.mp4`
** `-vcodec`：设定视频编码器；
* `ffmpeg -i out.ogv -s 640x480 -b 500k -vcodec h264 -r 29.97 -acodec libfaac -ab 48k -ac 2 out.mp4`
** `-s`：指定分辨率；`-b`：码率；`-r`：帧率；`-acodec`：设定音频编码器；`-ab`：音频码率；`-ac`：声道数；
** `-s 640:-1`：保持原始宽高比
* `ffmpeg -i music_flac.flac -acodec libmp3lame -ar 44100 -ab 320k -ac 2 music_flac_mp3.mp3`
* 网络流媒体下载：`ffmpeg -i "https://vdn.vzuu.com/SD/..." output.mp4`
** 流媒体地址：`"https://vdn.vzuu.com/SD/..."`

!!//2、提取音视频：//
* 提取音频：`ffmpeg -i mov_bbb.mp4 -acodec copy -vn output.aac`
** `copy`：保持原编码格式；`-vn`：不处理视频；`-i`：输入流；
* 提取视频：`ffmpeg -i input.mp4 -vcodec copy -an output.mp4`
** `-an`：不处理音频；
* 合并音视频：`ffmpeg -i a.m4a -i v.mp4 -c copy out.mp4`

!!//3、剪切：//
* 起始 + 时长：`ffmpeg -ss 00:00:15 -t 00:00:05 -i input.mp4 -vcodec copy -acodec copy output.mp4`
** `-ss`：开始时间；`-t`：切割时长；
* 起始 + 结束：`ffmpeg -ss 5 -to 45 -i input.mp4 -c copy -copyts output.mp4`
** `-to`：结束时间；
* //`关键帧技术`://
** `-ss` 放置在 `-i` 之前，关键帧技术的`起止时间`不准确
** `-copyts`：开启`关键帧技术` + 保留`时间戳`
* 录制Gif：`ffmpeg -i video.mp4 -ss 7.5 -to 8.5 -s 640x320 -r 15 video_gif.gif`

!!//4、[[FFmpeg合并]]：//
* `ffmpeg -i "concat:01.mp4|02.mp4|03.mp4" -c copy out.mp4`
** `-concat`：//concatenate// 串联

!!//5、[[FFmpeg音视频倍速]]：//
* 2倍速（视频）：`ffmpeg -i TheOrigin.mp4 -vf  "setpts=0.5*PTS" UpTheOrigin.mp4`
* 0.5倍速（视频）：`ffmpeg -i TheOrigin.mp4 -vf  "setpts=2*PTS" UpTheOrigin.mp4`
* 2倍速（音频）：`ffmpeg -i input.mkv -filter:a "atempo=2.0" -vn output.mkv`
* 0.5倍速（音频）：`ffmpeg -i input.mkv -af "atempo=0.5" -vn output.mkv`
* 同步调整：`ffmpeg -i imput.mp4  -filter_complex "[0:v]setpts=0.5*PTS[v];[0:a]atempo=2.0[a]" -map "[v]" -map "[a]" output_Acc.mp4`
* 同步调整：` ffmpeg -i Love1.mp4 -vf "setpts=0.5*PTS" -af "atempo=2.0" Love.mp4`







<<<
!!//[[FFmpeg]]：Fast Forward Moving Picture Experts Group//
!!//A complete, cross-platform solution to record, convert and stream audio and video. //
<<<

!!//FFmpeg对视频和音频播放速度，其调整原理不一样//
* 视频：修改`PTS`、`DTS`
** 2倍速（视频）：`ffmpeg -i TheOrigin.mp4 -vf  "setpts=0.5*PTS" UpTheOrigin.mp4`
** 0.5倍速（视频）：`ffmpeg -i TheOrigin.mp4 -vf  "setpts=2*PTS" UpTheOrigin.mp4`
* 音频：简单方法：`调整采样率`，该方法改变声色；一般：原音`重采样`、`差值`等
** 2倍速（音频）：`ffmpeg -i input.mkv -filter:a "atempo=2.0" -vn output.mkv`
** 0.5倍速（音频）：`ffmpeg -i input.mkv -af "atempo=0.5" -vn output.mkv`

!!//音视频同步调整//
* ` ffmpeg -i Love1.mp4 -vf "setpts=0.5*PTS" -af "atempo=2.0" Love.mp4`






<<<
!!//[[FFmpeg]]：Fast Forward Moving Picture Experts Group//
!!//A complete, cross-platform solution to record, convert and stream audio and video. //
<<<

!!//FFplay倍速播放//
* //音频过滤器实现倍速，atempo过滤器范围 [0.5，2]，若需4倍速，采用两个atempo过滤器//
** `ffplay later.mp3 -af atempo=2.0,atempo=2.0 -nodisp`
** 滤镜链使用";“分隔，滤镜链中滤镜使用”,"分隔

!!//淡入浅出效果//
* `ffmpeg -i later.mp3 -af "volume='if(lt(t,10),0.2,min(0.2+(t-10)/10*(1-0.2),1))':eval=frame" xxx.wav`<br>`ffmpeg -i later.mp3 -af "afade=t=in:ss=0:d=15,afade=t=out:st=30:d=15,volume=volume=0.3" -t 60 xxx.wav`<br>`ffplay later.mp3 -af "afade=t=in:ss=0:d=15,afade=t=out:st=30:d=15,volume=volume=0.3" `

!!//教材：《从0开始学习Github系列.pdf》、[[Git教程|https://www.softwhy.com/article-8478-1.html]]//

!!//1、Git下载//
* //[[Git下载地址|https://git-scm.com/downloads]]//
* 目录`D:/Git/bin`添加至`Path`
** `sh`
** `git`
** `bash`
* git程序版本：`git version`、`git --version`

!!//2、Git环境配置//
* 配置用户名、邮箱认证 `$ git config`
** `$ git config --global user.name "Mememori3476"`
** `$ git config --global user.email zhc1548886414@qq.com`
* 查看用户名、邮箱：`$ git config user.name`、`$ git config user.email`

!!//3、Git repository//
* 创建本地文件夹 > 右键 `Git Bash Here`
* `$ git init`，生成`.git`文件夹，初始化仓库 //Git repository//
* `$ git add .`，将工作区中所有文件添加至暂存区，临时保存
** `$ git rm --cached`，移除缓存
* `$ git commit -m "FirstTime push"`，将暂存区文件提交至本地仓库
** `commit`：提交；`-m`：代表提交信息
* `$ git log`，查看所有commit记录



!!//4、Git-Github建立SSH远程登陆协议//
* SSH网络协议，计算机之间的加密登陆，防止随便提交代码
* 创建SSH密钥：`$ ssh-keygen -t rsa -C "zhc1548886414@qq.com"`
** 生成的公钥位置：//C:\Users\Memento Mori\.ssh\`id_rsa.pub`//
** 密钥：//`id_rsa`//
* 进入个人Github > Setting > `SSH and GPG keys`
** new SSH keys > 复制`id_rsa.pub`文件内容
* 测试公钥正确性：`$ ssh -T git@github.com`
** _//You've successfully authenticated, but Github does not provide shell access//_，标识添加成功

!!//5、Push & Pull//
* 一般先进行`Pull`，后进行`Push`
* `Pull`：将远程仓库代码更新至本地
** `$ git pull origin master`
* `Push`：将本地代码推到远程仓库
** `$ git push origin master`，本地代码推到远程`master`分支


!!//5、Github提交代码//
* 方法1，Pull > Push
** 本地文件夹 > `Git Bash Here`
** `$ git clone git@github.com:Mememori3476/Mememori3476.github.io.git`
*** 将项目`Mememori3476.github.io.git` `clone`至本地，项目本身相当于git仓库，不需`git init`初始化
** 仅需在修改、添加文件后，进行`git add .` + `git commit -m "xxx"`
** `git push origin master`，实现代码提交

* 方法2，直接`Push`本地项目
** 切换至本地项目位置
** `$ git remote add origin git@github.com:Mememori3476/Mememori3476.github.io.git`，本地项目与Github项目关联
*** 添加远程仓库，地址：//git@github.com:Mememori3476/Mememori3476.github.io.git//
*** 仓库名：`origin`
** `git push origin master`，提交远程仓库


!!//6、Git分支//
* //创建//
** `$ git branch`，查看当前分支情况，默认`master`
** `$ git branch temp`，创建分支：Temp，此时内容同`master`一致
*** bash界面显示：`* master`：标识当前仍处于 `master` 分支
** `$ checkout temp`，切换至`temp`分支
** `$ checkuot -b temp`，新建`temp`分支，并切换至`temp`分支

* //合并//
** `$ checkout master`
** `$ git merge temp`

* //删除//
** `$ git branch -d temp`，删除分支`temp`（已合并至`master`）
** `$ git branch -D temp`，强制删除分支`temp`

* //Tag-不同版本对应不同代码//
** `$ git tag v1.0`，当前代码状态新建`v1.0`标签
** `$ git tag`，查看历史`tag`记录
** `$ git checkout v1.0`，切换至`v1.0 tag`代码状态









! [[Git与GitHub]]

* `$ git add .`，将工作区中所有文件添加至暂存区，临时保存
** `$ git rm --cached`，移除缓存
* `$ git commit -m "FirstTime push"`，将暂存区文件提交至本地仓库
** `commit`：提交；`-m`：代表提交信息
* `Push`：将本地代码推到远程仓库
** `$ git push origin master`，本地代码推到远程`master`分支







!! ''//字体效果 </font>//''
* 颜色：`<font color=#006633>娴啊娴</font>`，<font color=#006633>娴啊娴</font>
* 大小：`<font size="4">小娴娴</font>`，<font size="4">小娴娴</font>
* 字体：`<font style="font-family:楷体">娴啊娴</font>`，<font style="font-family:楷体">娴啊娴</font>
* 倾斜：`<i>小娴娴</i>`，<i>小娴娴</i>；`<em>小娴娴</em>`，<em>小娴娴</em>
* 加粗：`<b>小娴娴</b>`，<b>小娴娴</b>，`<strong>小娴娴</strong>`，<strong>小娴娴</strong>
* 下标：`娴啊娴<sub>[1]</sub>`，娴啊娴<sub>[1]</sub>
* 上标：`<sup>[2]</sup>小娴娴`，<sup>[2]</sup>小娴娴
* 删除：`<strike>删  除</strike>`，<strike>删  除</strike>

!!//[[Markdown Syntax for SimpleNote|https://simplenote.com/help/#markdown]]//
!!//[[Markdown教程|https://www.jianshu.com/p/191d1e21f7ed/]]//

!!//1、标题//
```markdown
# heading 1
## heading 2
### heading 3
```

!!//2、字体//
```markdown
*Italics*
**Bold**
***Italics and Bold***
~~Delete~~
```

!!//3、引用//
```markdown
>first referance
>>second referance
```

!!//4、分割线//
```markdonw
***
---
```

!!//5、图片//
```markdown
Embed an image:
![alt](https://path_to_image.png)
```

!!//6、超链接//
```markdown
Links: [Simplenote](https://simplenote.com/)
```


!!//7、无序列表//
* `+ `、`- `、`* ` 均可，注意符号后`空格`
```markdown
Lists:
+ Thing 1
- Thing 2
* Thing 3
```

!!//8、表格//
* 第二行分割表头、内容
** `-`，默认居左
** `:-:`，居中，`:`两边
** `-:`，居右，`:`右侧
```markdown
表头|表头|表头
-|:-:|-:
内容|内容|内容
内容|内容|内容
```

!!//9、代码//
* 反引号

```markdown
`代码内容`

(```)
  代码
  代码
(```)
```

!!''//特点：//'' 
* 优点：免除单个html文件，进行插件的拖拽……
* 缺点：仍需手动编辑 `tiddlywiki.info`文件

!! ''//Commander Server版配置：//''
* 下载 Commander github folder
* 将github folder/source文件夹复制进 文件夹 Tiddlywiki/plugin/kookma
* 编辑`tiddlywiki.info`文件
** `"kookma/commander"`
```json
{
	"plugins": [
		"tiddlywiki/codemirror",
		"kookma/commander"
	],
	"themes": [
		"tiddlywiki/vanilla",
		"tiddlywiki/snowwhite"
	],
    "languages": [
        "en-EN"
    ]
}
```

i. quit the server if it is runing,<br>
ii. put the `commander` folder into your local `plugins` folder under your wiki folder,<br>
iii. restart the server."""/>






<<<
!!! //''NodeJs 实现 TiddlyWiki 实时保存''//
<<<

!! //''[[Nodejs配置]]''//

!! ''//TiddlyWiki安装//''
* nodejs 安装 tiddlyWiki：//``npm install -g tiddlywiki``//
** <a class="badge-pill badge-info" target="_blank" href="https://github.com/Jermolene/TiddlyWiki5" > Tiddlywiki Github 网址</a>
** //`-g`// 表示：全局安装

!! ''//Nodejs运行TiddlyWiki//''
* 服务器新建 TiddlyWiki 文件夹：//``tiddlywiki xxx --init server``//
** 载入// index.html：`tiddlywiki xxx --load index.html`//
*** //index.html// 文件与 xxx文件夹，处于同一个目录下（或指明地址）
** 基于 xxx 启动 TiddlyWiki 服务：//``tiddlywiki xxx --listen``//
*** 默认地址 //[[http://127.0.0.1:8080/|http://127.0.0.1:8080/]]//
** 多端口运行：`tiddlywiki xxx --listen port=8090`
*** 多端口地址 //http://127.0.0.1:8090/ //

<<translink """Tiddlywiki保存html""">>







!! ''//Nodejs配置//''
* <a class="badge-pill badge-info " target="_blank" href="https://nodejs.org/en/download/" > Nodejs下载</a>

* nodejs 默认进行 node 和 npm 的配置
* 版本查看：//``node -v`` 和 ``npm -v`` 和 ``tiddlywiki --version``//（cmd在node_global文件夹下）
* nodejs 环境配置（node_cache、node_global 文件夹地址）
** nodejs 安装目录下，创建文件夹 node_cache、node_global
** cmd 下进行 //`npm config`//
***// `npm config set cache "D:\nodejs\node_cache"`//
***// `npm config set prefix "D:\nodejs\node_global"`//
*** 若希望回复默认值，删除文件 //`C:\Users\xxx\.npmrc`//
** 环境变量设置
*** `新建` 系统变量，变量名：//`NODE_PATH`//；变量值：//`D:\nodejs\node_modules`//
*** `修改` 用户变量，变量名：//`Path`//；变量值：//`C:\Users\xxx\AppData\Roaming\npm` ——> `D:\nodejs\node_global`//

!! //第一层：内容笔记//
* 所有东西全部归纳进入 Archive
* 全文搜索、//''`标签`''//搜索足以处理较小的档案
** 标签成为进入档案的入口
* 随着笔记量的增多，搜索一个标签将会得到很多的笔记 
** //''`概要式笔记`''//，概括笔记的主要思想，概括该主题下最重要的笔记


!! //第二层：结构化笔记//
* 类似于 //''`Table of Contents`''//，目录
* 有两层：
** 内容：//''`tiny`''//，小片段形式
** 结构化笔记：//''`目录`''//形式
* 功能同 Tag 一致，均指向笔记

** render all non-system tiddlers using the static template for tiddlers into a static output folder in the current wiki / edition folder in plain text format

!! //rendertiddler//
* ''Syntax：`--rendertiddler <title> <filename> [<type>] [<template>] [<name>] [<value>]`''
* `tiddlywiki mememori3476 --rendertiddler 至爱时刻 "zhiai.html" "text/plain" $:/core/templates/static.tiddler.html`

* `[!is[system]]`：非系统 Tiddlers

!! `||` //''触发自动补全''//
* `"startOffset" : 2`，表示光标放置在`第2个`元素后

```json
{
      "pattern": "||",
      "filter": "[all[tiddlers]!is[system]]",
      "start": "[[|",
      "end": "]]",
      "startOffset" : 2
}
```

!! ''//转义符号`\`//''

```json
{
"pattern": "<tr",
"filter": "[all[tiddlers]!is[system]]",
"start": "<<translink \"\"\"",
"end": "\"\"\" >>"
}
```

!! ''//自动导出html//''
* 导出至：//''`Backup`''//
* [[bat获取系统时间]]

```bash
@echo off
title Wiki_render
color 6
echo please close wiki and start Syncs
pause
d:
cd d:/temp/nodejs/node_global
tiddlywiki mememori --render "[[ToDo]]" "" "text/plain" $:/core/save/all & d: & cd d:/desktop & start TiddlyBackupGithub.bat & timeout /T 5
```

```bash
@echo off
title TiddlyBackupGithub
color 4
echo Render Success !
copy /y D:\Temp\nodejs\node_global\Mememori\output\ToDo.html D:\TiddlyWiki\Solution\Tiddlywiki_mememori.html
copy /y D:\Temp\nodejs\node_global\Mememori\output\ToDo.html D:\TiddlyWiki\Mememori3476.github.io\wiki\index.html
move /y D:\Temp\nodejs\node_global\Mememori\output\ToDo.html D:\TiddlyWiki\Backup\Tiddlywiki_%Date:~2,2%.%Date:~5,2%.%Date:~8,2%.html
echo BackupCompleted and start github push
pause
```

!! //`<template>`//
* TiddlyWiki
** `$:/core/save/all`：相当于 保存TiddlyWiki至单html文件
** `$:/core/save/empty`：保存TiddlyWiki，但不保存Tiddlers，Plugins保留
** `$:/core/save/lazy-all`：相对于`empty`，保留Tiddlers的标题
** `$:/core/save/lazy-images`：相对于`all`，无图模式
* html
** `$:/core/templates/alltiddlers.template.html`：将所有 Tiddlers 转化为 单个html文件
** `$:/core/templates/static.template.html`：输出Home静态页面，保留CSS样式
** `$:/core/templates/static.tiddler.html`：输出静态页面，缺少CSS样式
* Text
** `$:/core/templates/server/static.tiddler.html`：纯文本保留，未指定编码
** `$:/core/templates/server/static.tiddler.wikitext`：相较于`static.tiddler.html`，仅保留`wikitext`
** `$:/core/templates/static.area`：输出所有Tiddlers名称
** `$:/core/templates/exporters/JsonFile`
** `$:/core/templates/html-tiddler`：该模版，未指定编码，缺少CSS样式

return [{type: "text", text: linkText}];

    attributes: {

    },

        type: "text",
        text: linkText
    }]
}];

<<<//
记录和组织信息的目的是为了可以 //''`再次使用`''//。记录信息的价值与其可以被重复使用的容易程度成正比。//
<<<
<<<//
条目（Tiddler）的哲学思想是，我们通过将信息分割为 //''`最小的语义上有意义的单元`''//，利用他们之间丰富的 //''`关系模型`''//，从而最大化信息的可复用性。然后，我们再通过 //''`聚合和构思`''// 来把片段编排在一起，以呈现具有叙述性的故事。//
<<<

<<<//
TiddlyWiki 渴望为条目（Tiddler）提供一种代数，一种表达和探索信息项之间关系的简洁方式。//
<<<

<<<
<a href="https://github.com/Jermolene/TiddlyWiki5" target="_blank" class="btn btn-info btn-sm">Jermolene_TiddlyWiki5</a>
<<<







* Confirm Changes to this Tiddler：`Ctrl + Enter`
* Monospaced character format（等距字符格式）：`Ctrl + M` <——效果
* Toggle the sidebar visibility（SliderBar Visible）：`Shift + Alt + S`
* SiderBar Search：`Ctrl + Shift + F`
* Advanced Search：`Ctrl + Shift + A`

---

* 创建链接`[[xxx]]`，`Shift + Alt + L`
* 引用文本`{{xxx}}`，`Shift + Alt + T`
* 文本拆分，`Crtl + E`






* 通过 Sidebar 拖拽
* 点击 Tag 拖拽






!!''//文章的拆解和复用，实质是[[Tiddlywiki基本准则]]的体现//'' 
<<<
<<translink """Tiddlywiki基本准则""">>
<<<

!!''//基本概念//''
* `Tiddler`：Tiny笔记，相当于`Zettel`，信息的最小化单元
* `Link`：链接，如链接到 Tiddlywiki 为标题的 Tiddler ——>[[TiddlyWiki]]，`[[Tiddlywiki]]`；仅保留链接
* `Transclusion`：嵌入标记，标记符：`{{{TiddlyWiki}}}`；链接 TiddlyWiki 的文本
* `Macro`：宏指令，相当于 `Link + Transclusion`，默认`Macro name：translink`

!! ''//文章拆解//''
* `Ctrl + E` 快捷键，Excise the selected text into a new Tiddler，将选中文本转移至新的 Tiddler；
* 选中 `Tag new tiddler with the title of this tiddler`，将拆解后的 Tiddler 设置 Tag，进行归档整理
* `Replace excised text with`，translink效果如下

<<translink """推荐Zettelkasten笔记系统""">>

!! ''//文章合并//''
* `[[TiddlyWiki]]`，建立链接
* `{{TiddlyWiki}}`，直接引用
* `<<translink """TiddlyWiki""">>`

!!//1、标题栏：//
* |`!xxx`|
* |`xxx`|`h`

|!Cell1 |!Cell2 |
|Cell3 |Cell3 |h
|Cell4|Cell5|


!!//2、左右对齐方式(`空格`)//
* 左对齐：|`left aligned  `|
* 右对齐：|`  right aligned`|
* 居中：|` center aligned `|

| Alignment Syntax |h
|Left Align |
| Right Align|
| Center content |
|Memento Mori_Personal Notebook|


!!//3、垂直对齐//
* 上对齐：|` ^xxx `|
* 下对齐：|` ,xxx `|
* 手动换行：`<br>`
| Alignment Syntax |<|<|h
|^top left |^ top<br>center |^ top right|
|middle left | middle<br>center | middle right|
|,bottom left |, bottom<br>center |, bottom right|

!!//4、单元格合并//
* 向左合并：|`<`|
* 向右合并：|`>`|
* 合并一个已上：|`~`|
|Cell1 |Cell2 |Cell3 |Cell4 |
|Cell5 |Cell6 |Cell7 |<|
|Cell5 |~|Cell7 |Cell8 |
|>|Cell9 |Cell10 |Cell11 |

!!//5、CSS指定、标题、页眉、页脚//
* CSS：| xxx | xxx |`k`
* 标题：| xx | xx |`h`
* 页脚：| xx | xx|`f`
* 表格名：| xx | xx |`c`

|This is the Example, Little Princess Xian|<|h
|myclass anotherClass|k
|Table1: This is a caption |c
|Cell1 |Cell2 |
|Cell3 |Cell3 |
|Header1|Header2|h
|Footer|Footer|f
